AllInventoryCompanyList is a List
    is primary
    title is "InventoryCompanies"
    initially display search
    Display Fields
        Company
            raise red alert when (IsOngoingGlobalAverageCostComputation)
                mouse over text is "Creating_\\Global_\\Average_\\CostProcessIsNotYetCompleteForThis_\\Company"
        Name
        GlobalLocationNumber
        ItemGroup
        CostingMethod
        CurrentYear
        CurrentPeriod
    restrict action AttachToPricingGroup
